	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001016_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'--> 
<!--Hand 01 11 top left-->
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><placeName>57 Sloane <choice><abbr>St</abbr><expan>Street</expan></choice></placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="words"/>8<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> May 1857</p><!--hand 02 68011 superscripted B right margin-->
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear Sir</p>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="words"/>I am extremely 
<lb/>sorry to find that 
<lb/>the time I intended 
<lb/>to be in Scotland 
<lb/>is so near and 
<lb/>the work which 
<lb/>must be done 
<lb/>before I can 
<lb/>move is so great 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001016_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'--> 
<lb/>I must inflict 
<lb/>a disappointment 
<lb/>on my friends 
<lb/>I am very sorry 
<lb/>for it but my 
<lb/>engagements 
<lb/>with <persName>my publisher</persName>
<lb/>will prevent 
<lb/>me coming as 
<lb/>soon as I intended 
<lb/>&amp; I cannot <unclear cert="low">a </unclear>present 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001016_0003"/><!--pb/@n='3'--> 
<lb/>name a day but 
<lb/>I am making <unclear cert="high">exertions</unclear>
<lb/>to get through with 
<lb/>my work as 
<lb/>soon as possible 
<lb/>I shall let you 
<lb/>know the 
<lb/>moment I see 
<lb/>my way clear 
<lb/>to visit Scotland</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>Believe me</p>
<lb/><p>yours truly</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>D. Livingstone</p>
			
